## Command Quick Reference

| Action | Command |
|---|---|
| SSH in | `ssh root@138.197.9.139` |
| Attach to session | `tmux attach -t stream` |
| New session (if gone) | `tmux new -s stream` |
| Start radio | `ffmpeg -re -stream_loop -1 -i HoldtLoop.mp4 -c:v copy -c:a copy -f flv rtmp://live.restream.io/live/re_10860387_75ea120b5509c4a2572f` |
| Stop radio | Press **Q** in tmux session |
| Upload new video | `scp HoldtLoop.mp4 root@138.197.9.139:/root/` |
| Check disk space | `df -h` |
| Check running processes | `ps aux \| grep ffmpeg` |
| Kill FFmpeg if stuck | `pkill ffmpeg` |

