## Architecture Diagram

```
┌──────────────┐     RTMP      ┌───────────┐    Forward    ┌─────────┐
│ VPS (FFmpeg) │───────────────→│ Restream  │──────────────→│ YouTube │
│ $6/mo DO     │               │ Standard  │               │         │
│ stream-copy  │               │ $16/mo    │               │         │
└──────────────┘               └───────────┘               └─────────┘
       ↕ (manual swap)              ↑
┌──────────────┐     RTMP           │
│ Laptop (OBS) │────────────────────┘
│ Live streams  │  (same ingest point)
└──────────────┘
```

Only one encoder streams at a time. Kill VPS → start OBS. Stop OBS → restart VPS.

